00:25.700 --> 00:29.900
Mouth full of dust, I swallow it down.
00:33.540 --> 00:37.880
Same cracked mirror in a different town.
00:39.840 --> 00:43.920
Wrote my name with a paint peel fan.
00:44.220 --> 00:47.720
Watched it fade like it never had been.
00:48.020 --> 00:51.460
I kept the noise where I couldn't get out.
00:52.100 --> 00:55.340
Buried it deep under muscle and doubt.
00:55.700 --> 01:04.520
Every word I should have said sits like a wire inside my chest.
01:04.900 --> 01:12.020
Twist and pull, feels nothing left.
01:12.660 --> 01:17.220
Self-proclaimed prophet and God.
01:20.220 --> 01:25.220
Spitting sermons I never bought.
01:25.700 --> 01:30.840
Face in the dirt, teeth in the mud.
01:31.140 --> 01:36.700
Swore I was clean, I'm covered in it.
01:51.820 --> 01:55.620
Hands in my pockets, I circle the block.
01:55.700 --> 01:59.740
Counting the cracks in the sidewalk chalk.
01:59.900 --> 02:03.200
Voices I buried start leaking through.
02:03.760 --> 02:07.160
Sound like a younger unbroken you.
02:07.500 --> 02:11.190
I hear him call, but I don't turn back.
02:11.320 --> 02:15.520
Just drag his name through the gravel track.
02:15.780 --> 02:19.520
Every step I try to fake.
02:19.740 --> 02:23.440
Grinds that echo back awake.
02:23.440 --> 02:25.660
Pulls me under.
02:25.900 --> 02:29.740
I can't help but run.
02:29.740 --> 02:35.740
Self-proclaimed prophet and God.
02:35.740 --> 02:45.740
Spitting sermons I never bought.
02:46.060 --> 02:49.940
Face in the dirt, teeth in the mud.
02:50.140 --> 02:55.480
Swore I was clean, I'm covered in it.
02:55.700 --> 03:06.680
No one owns the blood I bled.
03:07.080 --> 03:10.620
No one wears the crown I shed.
03:10.620 --> 03:16.440
If I could see what I became, I'd choke it out.
03:16.540 --> 03:19.200
I'd say the name.
03:21.700 --> 03:23.600
Say the name.
03:25.700 --> 03:31.500
Say the name.
03:31.500 --> 03:39.080
The shame within.
03:39.080 --> 03:39.400
The shame within.
03:53.700 --> 03:55.680
Self-proclaimed.
03:55.700 --> 03:58.700
Profit in God.
04:01.800 --> 04:08.340
Spending summons I never bought.
04:08.340 --> 04:10.440
Face in the dirt.
04:10.760 --> 04:12.320
Teeth in the mud.
04:12.660 --> 04:14.340
Swore I was clean.
04:14.540 --> 04:17.640
I'm covered in it.
04:17.770 --> 04:19.200
Say the name.
04:19.680 --> 04:21.020
Let it in.
04:21.480 --> 04:24.660
Drag it up from under skin.
04:25.700 --> 04:26.950
Say the name.
04:27.220 --> 04:28.360
Don't pretend.
04:29.260 --> 04:33.040
You were never innocent.
